bluecoatSGProxyMIB.name: bluecoatSGProxyMIB
bluecoatSGProxyMIB.description: The BLUECOAT-SG-PROXY-MIB provides system information and statistics for a BlueCoat SG proxy appliance.

sgProxyAdmin.name: sgProxyAdmin
sgProxyAdmin.description: The contact responsible for the administration of the proxy. Usually a name and email address.

sgProxySerialNumber.name: sgProxySerialNumber
sgProxySerialNumber.description: Hardware serial number of the proxy appliance.

sgProxyCpuCoreTable.name: sgProxyCpuCoreTable
sgProxyCpuCoreTable.description: This table lists the various cpu statistics.

sgProxyCpuUpTime.name: sgProxyCpuUpTime
sgProxyCpuUpTime.description: The amount of time the proxy has been running since boot, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuBusyTime.name: sgProxyCpuBusyTime
sgProxyCpuBusyTime.description: The amount of busy CPU time since boot, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuIdleTime.name: sgProxyCpuIdleTime
sgProxyCpuIdleTime.description: The amount of idle CPU time since boot, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuUpTimeSinceLastAccess.name: sgProxyCpuUpTimeSinceLastAccess
sgProxyCpuUpTimeSinceLastAccess.description: The amount of time the proxy has been running since the last SNMP access to this value, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuBusyTimeSinceLastAccess.name: sgProxyCpuBusyTimeSinceLastAccess
sgProxyCpuBusyTimeSinceLastAccess.description: The amount of busy CPU time since the last SNMP access to this value, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuIdleTimeSinceLastAccess.name: sgProxyCpuIdleTimeSinceLastAccess
sgProxyCpuIdleTimeSinceLastAccess.description: The amount of idle CPU time since the last SNMP access to this value, in milliseconds. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuBusyPerCent.name: sgProxyCpuBusyPerCent
sgProxyCpuBusyPerCent.description: The busy CPU time as a percentage, averaged over one minute. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyCpuIdlePerCent.name: sgProxyCpuIdlePerCent
sgProxyCpuIdlePerCent.description: The idle CPU time as a percentage, averaged over one minute. This is no longer functional. Use sgProxyCpuTable instead.

sgProxyStorage.name: sgProxyStorage
sgProxyStorage.description: The quantity of storage in use by the proxy in bytes.

sgProxyNumObjects.name: sgProxyNumObjects
sgProxyNumObjects.description: The number of objects currently held by the proxy.

sgProxyMemAvailable.name: sgProxyMemAvailable
sgProxyMemAvailable.description: The total memory available for use by the proxy, in bytes.

sgProxyMemCacheUsage.name: sgProxyMemCacheUsage
sgProxyMemCacheUsage.description: The memory used by the proxy for object caching, in bytes.

sgProxyMemSysUsage.name: sgProxyMemSysUsage
sgProxyMemSysUsage.description: The memory used by the proxy for system and support processes, in bytes.

sgProxyMemoryPressure.name: sgProxyMemoryPressure
sgProxyMemoryPressure.description: The proportion of memory used in total by the proxy, as a percentage of the total memory available.

sgProxyCpuCoreTableEntry.name: sgProxyCpuCoreTableEntry
sgProxyCpuCoreTableEntry.description: A cpuTable entry describes the current cpu statistics.

sgProxyCpuCoreUpTime.name: sgProxyCpuCoreUpTime
sgProxyCpuCoreUpTime.description: The amount of time the proxy has been running since boot, in milliseconds.

sgProxyCpuCoreBusyTime.name: sgProxyCpuCoreBusyTime
sgProxyCpuCoreBusyTime.description: The amount of busy CPU time since boot, in milliseconds.

sgProxyCpuCoreIdleTime.name: sgProxyCpuCoreIdleTime
sgProxyCpuCoreIdleTime.description: The amount of idle CPU time since boot, in milliseconds.

sgProxyCpuCoreUpTimeSinceLastAccess.name: sgProxyCpuCoreUpTimeSinceLastAccess
